Business Brief -- HealthSouth Rehabilitation Corp.:
   Firm, Continental Medical
   Sign a Merger Agreement
CHS's board will consist of the seven current members of
Continental Medical's board and four people to be designated
by HealthSouth, the companies said.
   Rocco A. Ortenzio, Continental Medical's chairman and
chief executive officer, will be chairman and chief executive
of the holding company. Richard M. Scrushy, HealthSouth's
chairman, will be vice chairman and a director of the holding
company and will also continue as president and chief
executive of the HealthSouth unit. Robert A. Ortenzio,
Continental Medical's president and chief operating officer,
will be president and chief operating officer of CHS.
   CHS will be based in Mechanicsburg, Pa., the current site
of Continental Medical.